CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

February 16, 2010

[Cite as 02/16/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-461.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2010-0164. State ex rel. McDougald v. Brunsman.

In Habeas Corpus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of habeas corpus. Upon consideration of relator’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
